{"tid":2103780,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消息指新蒲崗順豐門市再多3人現病徵 員工照返工恐引大爆發","createTime":"2020-07-11T12:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-12T08:51:00.000Z","uid":5195,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"84e9e438514e4ab3c9e367569e7b488d3d04ad32","tid":2103780,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:35:55.000Z","msg":"本港武漢肺炎疫情出現第三波爆發。順豐速運昨（10日）確認有一名隸屬新蒲崗分店的外判司機初步確診，該分店即時停業消毒，但《蘋果》今獲悉，最少3名來自同一分店的後勤主管級員工，相繼出現發燒等相關病徵，今日自行請假求醫。<br />\n<br />\n有該區現職員工稱，資方無為同店另外近30名員工設特別上班安排，須如常上班。另有前職員透露，員工今被調派其他場所，包括俗稱「大倉」的青衣中轉場，他憂做法引致公司內大爆發，甚至將病毒「派送」至全港。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》正向順豐速運查詢以上消息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200711/5YZJKSCUJZEBKFHPTDHGAASUOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200711%2F5YZJKSCUJZEBKFHPTDHGAASUOI%2F&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyLtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=2df16aa8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200711%2F5YZJKSCUJZEBKFHPTDHGAASUOI%2F&h=febe60d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200711/5YZJKSCUJZEBKFHPTDHGAASUOI/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b3236fb7a32ed60de30f8e117b370edf2c036e","tid":2103780,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:36:44.000Z","msg":"順豐運毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8137fbf98149a11bef0e912700b1e3acccd2b3b8","tid":2103780,"uid":3381,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:37:49.000Z","msg":"順豐好多派貨員都唔戴口罩<br />\n一開門奶嘢"},{"pid":"fb31264a2aaa79ffb89ed5570b58952a1b6c0600","tid":2103780,"uid":63934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T12:38:57.000Z","msg":"唔用順豐了"},{"pid":"2b863099232cb093fb79c03c8cfa07054e2ed9cd","tid":2103780,"uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8137fbf98149a11b